{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_06_01",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……1、2、3、4……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスライブに向けて練習にも熱が入っているな\n……しかし、いつもより動きが硬い気がするが……",
      "startTime": 9.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、調子が良くないようだが何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 15.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、少し疲れが溜まっているのかもしれません",
      "startTime": 19.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "今度、学校でクリスマス会をやるんですが\n私も生徒会長として手伝うことになったんです",
      "startTime": 27.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの練習、生徒会の通常業務、期末テストの勉強\nそれにクリスマス会の準備で休む暇がなくて……",
      "startTime": 37.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。あまり無理しないようにな\nもし俺に手伝えることがあれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 45.6000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "手伝えることですか？\nでは、一つお尋ねしてもよろしいでしょうか",
      "startTime": 51.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはクリスマスに\nどんなプレゼントをもらったら嬉しいですか？",
      "startTime": 56.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は心のこもった物なら何をもらっても嬉しいよ",
      "startTime": 59.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、当たり障りのない面白みのない答えですね",
      "startTime": 63.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "辛辣だな……\nそれで、どうして急にそんなことを聞いたんだ？",
      "startTime": 71.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマス会でプレゼント交換をするので\n各自でプレゼントを持ち寄ることになったんです",
      "startTime": 77.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "それでどんな物が喜ばれるか\n参考にしようと思ってみんなに聞いているんです",
      "startTime": 83.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。ちなみに他のみんなはなんて答えたんだ？",
      "startTime": 86.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "千紗はTシャツがいいと言っていました。自分では\n選ばないデザインの服を見るのが刺激になるそうです",
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "それを聞いて、私も自分で選んだTシャツを\nプレゼントにしようと思ったのですが……",
      "startTime": 101.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "なぜか千紗に止められてしまって……",
      "startTime": 103.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "千紗の提案通りにしたのに\n止められるなんて意味が分かりません",
      "startTime": 109.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど……\n他のメンバーには聞いてみたのか？",
      "startTime": 114.9333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんは「私の生写真を配れば\nみんな大喜びですわ」って言い出して……",
      "startTime": 120.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんが「それなら私は琴乃ちゃんの生写真が\nいいな～」って言い出して……",
      "startTime": 127.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃんが「私はドーナツがいい！」って言い出して\n収拾がつかなくなりました",
      "startTime": 133.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなのことは尊敬していますが\n時々ちょっとズレたことを言ったりするんですよね",
      "startTime": 138.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで考えてくれたのは嬉しかったんですが\n結局、私は何をプレゼントしたらいいんでしょうか……",
      "startTime": 145.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……。沙季は読書が好きだから\n自分の好きな本をプレゼントしてみるのはどうだ？",
      "startTime": 153.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "それはいい考えですね、もらった人が\nその本を好きになってくれたら私も嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 159.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど最近読んで感銘を受けた本があるので\nあれをプレゼントにしましょう",
      "startTime": 166.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それはどういう本なんだ？",
      "startTime": 168.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "数学の参考書です\nそれがとても分かりやすくてオススメなんです",
      "startTime": 173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "期末試験も近いですから、その本をもらった人は\nきっと喜ぶと思います",
      "startTime": 180.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5966.666666599991,
          "startTime": 182.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……\nちょっとズレてるというのはこういうことか",
      "startTime": 184.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 188.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "沙季？　楽屋でノートを広げて何をしているんだ？",
      "startTime": 190.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "私の出番まで時間があるので\n期末試験に向けてテスト勉強をしています",
      "startTime": 196.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "本当は自分の部屋で集中してやりたいんですが\n最近は勉強する時間がなかなか取れなくて……",
      "startTime": 203.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "真面目なのはいいが、あまり根を詰め過ぎるなよ\n時には息抜きをすることも大事だからな",
      "startTime": 211.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。息抜きするにはどうしたらいいか\nしっかり考えてみます",
      "startTime": 218.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そういう姿勢が息抜きとほど遠いんだよな……\nもっと肩の力を抜いて気楽にお喋りでもしたらどうだ？",
      "startTime": 224.3333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
